    {"id":22,"question":"$(3x^2y-6xy^2) \\div 3xy$를 계산하면?","choices":["$x-2y$","$x+2y$","$x^2-2y$","$x-2y^2$","$3x-6y$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$3x^2y\\div 3xy=x$, $6xy^2\\div 3xy=2y$. 결과: $x-2y$"},
